LBERTA ENERGY CO, Calgary say e don do di preliminary prospectus for one out of evry common share.

Natural resources development mean sey dem go use am take repay long term debt wey be sey na 598 million (US$ 510.6 million) for di end of 1988.

Di company plan to raise between C$75 million and C$100 million from di sama according to one spokeswoman for Richardson Greenshields of Canada Ltd, lead underwriter.

Di shares go dey exchange for early November.

